WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 6=

00:01:23.980 --> 00:01:27.570
You're planning to tell Bei everything?

00:01:27.980 --> 00:01:28.930
Yeah.

00:01:30.290 --> 00:01:31.820
Including Jiang Yifan.

00:01:32.900 --> 00:01:34.490
You're involved in this.

00:01:35.050 --> 00:01:36.410
So I need to tell you first.

00:01:37.770 --> 00:01:39.900
Why bring it up all of a sudden?

00:01:40.850 --> 00:01:42.330
Yesterday, when I had dinner with Bei,

00:01:42.490 --> 00:01:43.570
we ran into Yu He.

00:01:47.620 --> 00:01:48.740
What did she say?

00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:50.130
Nothing much, really.

00:01:51.130 --> 00:01:52.380
But it scared me.

00:01:53.210 --> 00:01:54.570
If I could run into you two today,

00:01:54.690 --> 00:01:56.980
who knows who else I'll run into next?

00:01:57.850 --> 00:01:59.900
I don't want Bei to hear it from others.

00:02:00.490 --> 00:02:02.690
I should've been honest with him.

00:02:03.210 --> 00:02:05.410
If you've hided something,

00:02:05.850 --> 00:02:07.540
you might well hide it forever.

00:02:08.220 --> 00:02:09.940
If you love him, accept all of him.

00:02:09.950 --> 00:02:11.690
That's easier said than done.

00:02:12.660 --> 00:02:14.690
Why hurt him with the truth?

00:02:15.260 --> 00:02:17.100
So hiding it doesn't hurt him?

00:02:17.260 --> 00:02:19.690
I mean, don't go too far.

00:02:20.220 --> 00:02:21.170
It's exhausting.

00:02:21.380 --> 00:02:22.220
Xi.

00:02:22.660 --> 00:02:24.130
This lady's here to see you.

00:02:24.820 --> 00:02:27.170
Sorry, do I know you?

00:02:27.290 --> 00:02:29.010
I'm in a rush, so I'll keep it short.

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:30.450
Miss Guan sent me here.

00:02:30.850 --> 00:02:32.500
I'd like to discuss something with you.

00:02:34.610 --> 00:02:35.820
Miss Zhao.

00:02:36.410 --> 00:02:38.130
Guan didn't tell you, did she?

00:02:38.850 --> 00:02:40.060
I'm afraid I can't help you.

00:02:40.450 --> 00:02:41.820
She did mention it to me.

00:02:42.060 --> 00:02:43.220
But I think

00:02:43.450 --> 00:02:45.170
there's nothing we can't talk through.

00:02:45.500 --> 00:02:46.850
If I'm guessing right,

00:02:47.010 --> 00:02:48.380
your husband has been cheating.

00:02:48.890 --> 00:02:50.380
And you've got no proof.

00:02:51.260 --> 00:02:53.170
I can't be the proof you're looking for.

00:02:54.660 --> 00:02:56.170
You came for the wrong person.

00:02:57.410 --> 00:02:58.570
You need a lawyer.

00:02:59.130 --> 00:02:59.970
How about this?

00:03:00.100 --> 00:03:01.130
How much do you want?

00:03:01.380 --> 00:03:02.220
Name your price.

00:03:07.410 --> 00:03:09.500
Miss Zhao, let me walk you out.

00:03:12.260 --> 00:03:14.780
Don't act so high and mighty.

00:03:15.690 --> 00:03:16.980
I've seen your

00:03:17.450 --> 00:03:18.570
type before.

00:03:19.500 --> 00:03:22.060
All talk on the surface, but actually

00:03:23.130 --> 00:03:24.940
you're no better than a mistress.

00:03:25.410 --> 00:03:26.940
Even worse than that.

00:03:27.820 --> 00:03:29.410
Always

00:03:29.780 --> 00:03:32.570
clinging to rich guys.

00:03:34.940 --> 00:03:36.290
Listen, lady,

00:03:36.410 --> 00:03:37.260
well,

00:03:37.260 --> 00:03:39.340
if you talk like that, I have to say.

00:03:39.450 --> 00:03:40.940
Forget who's worse here.

00:03:40.940 --> 00:03:41.890
Your marriage's unhappy.

00:03:41.890 --> 00:03:43.940
Maybe you should reflect yourself.

00:03:44.450 --> 00:03:45.850
Look at you, dressed up so fancy.

00:03:45.850 --> 00:03:47.010
You must've shopped a lot.

00:03:47.260 --> 00:03:49.220
What shirt size does your husband wear now?

00:03:49.450 --> 00:03:51.100
How much has his waist grown lately?

00:03:51.100 --> 00:03:52.980
When did you last buy him socks?

00:03:53.130 --> 00:03:53.980
Do you even know?

00:03:54.130 --> 00:03:55.410
No, you don't.

00:03:55.660 --> 00:03:56.730
You only know if the Birkin

00:03:56.730 --> 00:03:57.850
stitch is inside or out,

00:03:57.980 --> 00:03:59.820
the 2.55 bag's buckle gold or silver.

00:04:00.130 --> 00:04:01.540
You also know when your husband's

00:04:01.540 --> 00:04:02.660
WeChat is most active,

00:04:02.780 --> 00:04:04.890
and if anyone calls him late at night?

00:04:05.170 --> 00:04:07.570
Push too hard and things might snap back.

00:04:07.820 --> 00:04:09.260
Give him some space.

00:04:09.450 --> 00:04:11.610
Instead of hiring someone to test him,

00:04:11.780 --> 00:04:13.060
why not spend more time

00:04:13.060 --> 00:04:14.220
treating him better

00:04:14.340 --> 00:04:16.700
and trying to save your marriage.

00:04:16.900 --> 00:04:17.900
What's that smell?

00:04:17.900 --> 00:04:19.460
That cheap perfume smells awful.

00:04:19.460 --> 00:04:20.300
What are you doing?

00:04:20.730 --> 00:04:22.180
- Can you afford it?
- Miss Zhao.

00:04:22.650 --> 00:04:23.850
If you don't want your husband

00:04:23.850 --> 00:04:25.100
to find out about this,

00:04:26.730 --> 00:04:28.490
I'd suggest you be more careful.

00:04:34.050 --> 00:04:34.930
Fine.

00:04:36.050 --> 00:04:37.250
Really fine.

00:04:37.540 --> 00:04:38.700
Take care.

00:04:49.410 --> 00:04:50.610
Does this happen often?

00:04:51.700 --> 00:04:53.370
They couldn't find this place before.

00:04:54.340 --> 00:04:55.780
Consider this a warning.

00:04:56.250 --> 00:04:57.090
A warning?

00:04:57.860 --> 00:04:58.900
Someone's threatening you?

00:04:59.610 --> 00:05:01.100
That's why you're telling Bei.

00:05:03.140 --> 00:05:04.370
Thanks for today.

00:05:06.410 --> 00:05:07.290
If you tell him,

00:05:07.290 --> 00:05:08.850
what if he breaks up with you?

00:05:13.930 --> 00:05:15.610
Then tell me what to do.

00:05:21.100 --> 00:05:22.410
Is there any other way?

00:05:27.220 --> 00:05:29.170
I don't want him to see what happened today.

00:05:31.580 --> 00:05:33.140
If he truly cares about me,

00:05:33.900 --> 00:05:34.980
maybe…

00:05:41.100 --> 00:05:42.700
I don't want to hide this from him.

00:05:45.290 --> 00:05:46.490
I love him.

00:05:50.050 --> 00:05:51.930
But he hates Jiang Yifan so much.

00:05:52.780 --> 00:05:55.020
If he finds out I'm Jiang Yifan,

00:05:57.490 --> 00:05:58.900
will he hate me too?

00:06:11.460 --> 00:06:12.410
I don't know.

00:06:20.780 --> 00:06:21.810
Let me tell you.

00:06:22.610 --> 00:06:24.340
A girl once told me,

00:06:24.900 --> 00:06:26.220
when you love someone,

00:06:26.540 --> 00:06:27.980
right and wrong don't matter anymore.

00:06:28.930 --> 00:06:30.220
Just love him.

00:06:32.410 --> 00:06:34.410
Until he doesn't care about your past.

00:06:35.290 --> 00:06:37.140
Even when he knows your worst deeds,

00:06:38.540 --> 00:06:40.050
he still can't resist you.

00:06:42.340 --> 00:06:43.180
Alright?

00:06:56.220 --> 00:06:57.460
Thank you.

00:06:59.540 --> 00:07:01.100
Hey, relax.

00:07:01.810 --> 00:07:03.290
He'll be just like me.

00:07:03.780 --> 00:07:04.700
No.

00:07:04.700 --> 00:07:06.410
He'll understand you better than I do.

00:07:31.410 --> 00:07:32.340
(Baby,)

00:07:32.610 --> 00:07:34.410
(they say giving flowers on Valentine's Day)

00:07:34.410 --> 00:07:36.250
(is just cheesy, predictable.)

00:07:36.810 --> 00:07:38.780
(So on this ordinary day,)

00:07:38.980 --> 00:07:40.900
(I still want to share my love with you.)

00:07:41.700 --> 00:07:42.900
(May every day with me around)

00:07:43.250 --> 00:07:44.340
(bring you happiness.)

00:07:48.260 --> 00:07:49.100
(Lun)

00:07:57.140 --> 00:07:57.980
Hey.

00:07:58.490 --> 00:07:59.810
I got the flowers.

00:08:00.980 --> 00:08:02.250
Why do you always act like a kid

00:08:02.250 --> 00:08:03.410
whenever you get a gift?

00:08:03.780 --> 00:08:05.460
These are really beautiful.

00:08:05.660 --> 00:08:06.900
This should be the second-best

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:08.730
gift I've ever gotten.

00:08:09.540 --> 00:08:10.580
Then what's the first?

00:08:10.850 --> 00:08:11.700
Take a guess.

00:08:12.460 --> 00:08:13.580
Of course it's you.

00:08:15.930 --> 00:08:16.780
Silly.

00:08:16.980 --> 00:08:19.050
I'm with a client now. Talk later.

00:08:19.180 --> 00:08:21.460
(Everlasting Flower 3)

00:08:23.050 --> 00:08:23.890
Oh.

00:08:26.730 --> 00:08:27.900
Dinner tonight?

00:08:28.140 --> 00:08:30.140
Got clients tonight too.

00:08:30.270 --> 00:08:31.370
I'll find you when I'm done.

00:08:32.010 --> 00:08:33.730
Alright, bye.

00:08:35.130 --> 00:08:36.010
Bye.

00:08:50.460 --> 00:08:56.300
(Liang's Florist)

00:09:09.450 --> 00:09:11.300
- I don't want to lie to you.
- Just answer me.

00:09:12.300 --> 00:09:13.420
Are you married?

00:09:18.980 --> 00:09:20.100
I don't want to lie to you.

00:09:22.850 --> 00:09:23.820
It's just if I say it,

00:09:23.820 --> 00:09:24.770
you'll get hurt.

00:09:24.900 --> 00:09:25.770
I don't know how to...

00:09:25.770 --> 00:09:26.940
Are you married?

00:09:41.980 --> 00:09:42.820
Hello.

00:09:42.940 --> 00:09:44.340
Hello, is this

00:09:44.460 --> 00:09:45.820
Mr. Lun's place?

00:09:46.700 --> 00:09:48.490
His cake order has arrived.

00:09:49.220 --> 00:09:50.850
Oh, thank you.

00:09:51.530 --> 00:09:52.370
Seriously.

00:09:52.500 --> 00:09:53.850
Going all out for the anniversary.

00:10:11.250 --> 00:10:12.460
Yes, I'm married.

00:10:19.420 --> 00:10:20.300
Alright.

00:10:21.580 --> 00:10:22.580
We're done here.

00:10:22.700 --> 00:10:23.540
Mingming.

00:10:23.700 --> 00:10:24.980
Mingming, Mingming.

00:10:24.980 --> 00:10:25.820
Let go!

00:10:25.980 --> 00:10:27.460
I only love you. Can't you see?

00:10:27.650 --> 00:10:28.490
Right.

00:10:28.980 --> 00:10:29.850
Every time before,

00:10:29.850 --> 00:10:31.370
when I saw you with another woman,

00:10:31.370 --> 00:10:32.940
I'd lie to myself the same way.

00:10:33.220 --> 00:10:34.420
But now you tell me,

00:10:35.010 --> 00:10:36.770
how am I supposed to lie to myself now?

00:10:36.940 --> 00:10:37.850
Wait, listen to me.

00:10:38.770 --> 00:10:40.370
Mingming, it's been ten years for us.

00:10:40.730 --> 00:10:41.770
Back when we broke up,

00:10:42.180 --> 00:10:43.610
I thought my life was over.

00:10:44.370 --> 00:10:45.650
But then I met you again.

00:10:47.340 --> 00:10:49.130
I realized I never truly forgot you.

00:10:50.060 --> 00:10:50.940
I love you.

00:10:52.850 --> 00:10:54.370
I thought nothing'd change between us.

00:10:54.580 --> 00:10:56.060
Nothing would change?

00:10:57.010 --> 00:10:58.850
Am I really that kind of person
in your eyes?

00:10:59.770 --> 00:11:01.540
Mingming.

00:11:01.730 --> 00:11:02.570
Mingming.

00:11:03.180 --> 00:11:04.060
Let me go!

00:11:04.340 --> 00:11:05.180
I love you.

00:11:05.300 --> 00:11:06.580
You're the only one I truly love.

00:11:09.130 --> 00:11:10.130
You love me?

00:11:10.610 --> 00:11:12.490
You turned me into a homewrecker!

00:11:13.340 --> 00:11:14.370
Oh, really.

00:11:14.370 --> 00:11:16.060
This guy is such a jerk.

00:11:16.060 --> 00:11:17.130
Nice hit.

00:11:17.700 --> 00:11:18.980
- Too soft.
- Exactly.

00:11:18.980 --> 00:11:20.850
He deserves worse.

00:11:25.060 --> 00:11:25.900
Pass it.

00:11:26.370 --> 00:11:27.280
- Over here!
- Give it to me!

00:11:27.280 --> 00:11:28.280
Defend! Defend!

00:11:29.940 --> 00:11:31.970
♪At night♪

00:11:31.970 --> 00:11:36.560
♪I wonder if it will go away♪

00:11:37.840 --> 00:11:39.870
♪At dawn♪

00:11:39.870 --> 00:11:45.030
♪I wonder if I will be okay♪

00:11:45.940 --> 00:11:52.850
♪I lie awake♪

00:11:55.580 --> 00:11:56.740
(Lun)

00:11:57.115 --> 00:12:01.145
♪Thinking about how to stay in sane♪

00:12:01.170 --> 00:12:02.740
(Add to Blacklist)

00:12:02.740 --> 00:12:09.090
♪I lie awake♪

00:12:09.090 --> 00:12:12.970
♪Thinking there's nothing I could say♪

00:12:13.220 --> 00:12:17.720
♪Only to lie and lie awake♪

00:12:17.850 --> 00:12:18.690
Come in.

00:12:19.370 --> 00:12:20.490
Bei, you wanna see me?

00:12:20.600 --> 00:12:21.510
Come.

00:12:21.700 --> 00:12:22.580
Come.

00:12:25.580 --> 00:12:26.490
Have a seat.

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:36.890
Here.

00:12:36.890 --> 00:12:37.820
Thanks.

00:12:42.950 --> 00:12:43.810
Mingming.

00:12:43.810 --> 00:12:44.700
Hmm?

00:12:44.700 --> 00:12:46.370
Don't take my words the wrong way.

00:12:47.610 --> 00:12:48.700
I just want to ask,

00:12:49.060 --> 00:12:50.130
how are things with Sen?

00:12:50.820 --> 00:12:51.700
Pretty good.

00:12:52.730 --> 00:12:53.570
Uh.

00:12:55.340 --> 00:12:56.420
But actually…

00:12:57.370 --> 00:12:58.890
You're not together, are you?

00:13:00.980 --> 00:13:02.130
Did he tell you that?

00:13:03.220 --> 00:13:04.850
I could tell when he brought you here.

00:13:05.890 --> 00:13:06.730
Oh.

00:13:07.220 --> 00:13:08.060
Right.

00:13:12.060 --> 00:13:13.010
So…

00:13:14.940 --> 00:13:15.940
You like someone else?

00:13:16.060 --> 00:13:16.940
Bei.

00:13:17.890 --> 00:13:19.530
The man next to her isn't Sen, right?

00:13:19.770 --> 00:13:20.770
What do you want to eat?

00:13:21.060 --> 00:13:22.850
Hotpot or steak?

00:13:24.300 --> 00:13:25.490
Hmm, how about steak?

00:13:25.490 --> 00:13:26.650
There's a new place nearby.

00:13:29.820 --> 00:13:30.660
Mm.

00:13:33.850 --> 00:13:35.060
I've liked him

00:13:36.340 --> 00:13:37.940
for a long, long time.

00:13:38.530 --> 00:13:39.400
Catch it!

00:13:43.060 --> 00:13:44.580
Maybe everyone's first love

00:13:44.890 --> 00:13:46.530
starts as a secret crush.

00:13:47.940 --> 00:13:49.100
Some people say

00:13:49.610 --> 00:13:52.370
the hardest thing is mutual crushing.

00:13:53.100 --> 00:13:54.300
But I don't think so.

00:13:55.700 --> 00:13:58.340
That's the sweetest thing in the world.

00:14:08.980 --> 00:14:09.820
Hey.

00:14:15.340 --> 00:14:16.610
Would you like

00:14:18.420 --> 00:14:19.490
to be my girlfriend?

00:14:36.980 --> 00:14:38.340
First date.

00:14:39.820 --> 00:14:41.010
First time holding hands.

00:14:42.530 --> 00:14:43.890
First hug.

00:14:44.580 --> 00:14:45.580
First kiss.

00:14:47.730 --> 00:14:49.730
He fulfilled all my imaginations about love.

00:14:57.980 --> 00:14:59.490
I loved listening to Jay Chou.

00:14:59.700 --> 00:15:00.890
He only listened to JJ Lin.

00:15:01.180 --> 00:15:02.850
Still, he could sing every Jay Chou song

00:15:02.850 --> 00:15:04.220
and make it sound amazing.

00:15:08.850 --> 00:15:10.010
We used to walk hand in hand

00:15:10.220 --> 00:15:12.490
through every corner of the city.

00:15:13.340 --> 00:15:14.730
He swore that once he had money,

00:15:14.730 --> 00:15:16.340
he'd take me to Prague Square,

00:15:16.610 --> 00:15:18.220
and to Santorini to watch the sunrise.

00:15:19.580 --> 00:15:21.100
Almost my entire youth

00:15:21.580 --> 00:15:22.890
was tied to him.

00:15:25.340 --> 00:15:26.770
That's like textbook perfect love.

00:15:28.770 --> 00:15:29.730
Yeah.

00:15:30.060 --> 00:15:31.980
I'm lucky I got to experience that.

00:15:33.220 --> 00:15:34.530
If you've got someone you love,

00:15:35.250 --> 00:15:36.730
why didn't you just turn Sen down?

00:15:37.420 --> 00:15:38.890
It's over between me and that person,

00:15:39.460 --> 00:15:40.730
but I still need some time.

00:15:41.370 --> 00:15:42.420
All those years together...

00:15:42.420 --> 00:15:44.340
I can't just switch it off, right?

00:15:44.650 --> 00:15:46.060
How long do you expect him to wait?

00:15:48.300 --> 00:15:50.180
Until I can give him a new version of me,

00:15:50.340 --> 00:15:52.100
focused, with no lingering feelings.

00:15:52.450 --> 00:15:53.610
Only then would I deserve him.

00:15:54.130 --> 00:15:54.970
Right?

00:15:55.220 --> 00:15:56.610
I won't let him down.

00:15:56.820 --> 00:15:59.180
When the time comes, I'll give him my all.

00:16:01.300 --> 00:16:02.420
So, Bei,

00:16:03.250 --> 00:16:04.100
can you...

00:16:04.650 --> 00:16:06.300
pretend you don't know about this?

00:16:12.500 --> 00:16:13.370
Ms. Yu,

00:16:13.370 --> 00:16:14.650
could you check the sample?

00:16:14.660 --> 00:16:15.940
Anything need changing?

00:16:19.580 --> 00:16:21.340
I still think the sizing is off.

00:16:22.730 --> 00:16:24.370
I gave you her measurements.

00:16:24.580 --> 00:16:25.890
Why is it still made so small?

00:16:26.700 --> 00:16:27.540
Oh.

00:16:28.060 --> 00:16:28.900
Fix it.

00:16:29.370 --> 00:16:31.560
Yeah, true. Loose fit is in this year.

00:16:32.010 --> 00:16:33.820
Trends are impossible to keep up with.

00:16:33.980 --> 00:16:35.370
Don't talk to me about trends.

00:16:36.180 --> 00:16:37.650
Okay. I'll have the tailor adjust it.

00:16:37.650 --> 00:16:38.490
Go ahead.

00:16:38.820 --> 00:16:41.240
♪The haze within my heart♪

00:16:41.490 --> 00:16:42.890
Hello, delivery for you.

00:16:44.340 --> 00:16:45.250
I'll go grab it.

00:16:47.650 --> 00:16:49.250
Let me check that photo from earlier.

00:16:49.980 --> 00:16:51.980
- Okay.
- Yu, your delivery's here.

00:16:52.580 --> 00:16:53.650
Could you open it for me?

00:16:54.010 --> 00:16:54.850
Sure.

00:16:54.940 --> 00:16:59.250
♪I favor love, and I reflect on it♪

00:16:59.620 --> 00:17:01.770
♪Let black and white stand side by side♪

00:17:02.010 --> 00:17:03.580
LV, huh.

00:17:04.530 --> 00:17:06.380
What did you buy this time?

00:17:07.770 --> 00:17:08.610
Whoa.

00:17:09.490 --> 00:17:11.330
Is that this year's new style?

00:17:11.330 --> 00:17:13.330
- Yep.
- The silver's a limited edition.

00:17:13.460 --> 00:17:15.570
- Yep.
- Looks amazing.

00:17:17.940 --> 00:17:19.530
Hey, there's a card.

00:17:20.150 --> 00:17:22.310
♪I can't explain it♪

00:17:22.380 --> 00:17:23.290
Yu,

00:17:23.620 --> 00:17:25.490
I'm not good at picking gifts.

00:17:25.810 --> 00:17:27.770
And I'm no expert at sweet talk.

00:17:28.010 --> 00:17:30.180
I just want to see you happy.

00:17:30.810 --> 00:17:32.770
If this gift isn't your style,

00:17:33.010 --> 00:17:34.220
please don't be upset.

00:17:34.420 --> 00:17:36.090
And don't blame me for spending.

00:17:36.290 --> 00:17:39.140
I want a lifetime to understand you.

00:17:39.290 --> 00:17:41.220
To give you all the best I have.

00:17:41.530 --> 00:17:43.860
Just to fulfill that promise...

00:17:44.220 --> 00:17:46.290
I love you.

00:17:46.420 --> 00:17:47.620
Your clumsy husband.

00:17:47.770 --> 00:17:49.050
How's that clumsy?

00:17:49.180 --> 00:17:51.420
If I had a man like this,

00:17:51.530 --> 00:17:53.810
I'd be laughing in my sleep.

00:17:54.330 --> 00:17:55.380
See? It looks amazing.

00:17:55.490 --> 00:17:56.980
You'd probably lose sleep.

00:17:57.780 --> 00:17:59.590
♪I've been won over by love♪

00:17:59.590 --> 00:18:02.070
♪Then sold by love again♪

00:18:04.010 --> 00:18:05.180
Not busy, huh?

00:18:05.540 --> 00:18:07.410
♪Life feels pure as snow♪

00:18:07.420 --> 00:18:11.810
♪My eyes clouded
by the dust of life♪

00:18:13.010 --> 00:18:17.530
♪Hard to dream
of the old road again♪

00:18:18.730 --> 00:18:23.490
♪You ask when sorrow will fade♪

00:18:24.860 --> 00:18:30.010
♪See all causes,
yet no sign of the way back♪

00:18:31.770 --> 00:18:35.980
♪Lovebirds were never true lovers♪

00:18:36.660 --> 00:18:38.900
♪Lovebirds were...♪

00:18:44.290 --> 00:18:45.130
Hello?

00:18:47.330 --> 00:18:49.490
I'm at the shop writing a song. What's up?

00:18:50.980 --> 00:18:52.530
You got it already?

00:18:53.900 --> 00:18:54.770
Do you like it?

00:18:57.420 --> 00:18:58.620
You don't need

00:18:58.860 --> 00:19:00.010
to say thank you.

00:19:11.220 --> 00:19:12.140
Hey, Mom.

00:19:12.460 --> 00:19:13.460
I saw your post.

00:19:13.460 --> 00:19:15.290
Your husband bought you a bag?

00:19:15.730 --> 00:19:16.570
Yeah.

00:19:16.860 --> 00:19:18.660
So don't say he's stingy anymore.

00:19:18.660 --> 00:19:20.050
He's just stingy with others.

00:19:20.530 --> 00:19:21.490
All these years,

00:19:21.490 --> 00:19:23.350
he's never bought us anything.

00:19:23.490 --> 00:19:25.940
Do you think he actually cares about us?

00:19:26.090 --> 00:19:27.460
Mom, what's the matter?

00:19:27.570 --> 00:19:28.940
If he truly cared for you,

00:19:28.940 --> 00:19:30.770
you wouldn't have to work so hard.

00:19:31.250 --> 00:19:32.900
You're not young anymore.

00:19:33.220 --> 00:19:34.570
Take better care of yourself.

00:19:34.810 --> 00:19:36.250
Maybe think about having a kid.

00:19:37.490 --> 00:19:39.290
I like having my own things to do.

00:19:39.290 --> 00:19:41.010
What's that got to do with him?

00:19:41.010 --> 00:19:42.570
Of course it's connected.

00:19:43.400 --> 00:19:45.250
If you'd been with Hua back then,

00:19:46.050 --> 00:19:47.660
would you be struggling like this now?

00:19:48.570 --> 00:19:50.810
Our family knows Hua inside out.

00:19:51.430 --> 00:19:52.670
He's ambitious,

00:19:52.690 --> 00:19:53.990
respectful and mature.

00:19:54.020 --> 00:19:55.900
Most importantly, he treats you well.

00:19:56.490 --> 00:19:58.460
You wouldn't have to work so hard.

00:19:58.770 --> 00:20:00.420
I'd have grandkids by now.

00:20:00.570 --> 00:20:01.890
Alright, Mom, I'm busy.

00:20:01.890 --> 00:20:02.990
I gotta go now.

00:20:03.180 --> 00:20:04.020
Bye.

00:20:15.020 --> 00:20:15.860
(Moments)

00:20:16.330 --> 00:20:17.730
(48 New Messages)
(I'm so jealous.)

00:20:17.900 --> 00:20:19.330
- (The best husband!)
- (Gorgeous!)

00:20:19.770 --> 00:20:21.180
(I want one too.)

00:20:21.570 --> 00:20:22.610
(Limited edition!)

00:20:22.730 --> 00:20:24.620
(Can I borrow it for a few days?)

00:20:24.620 --> 00:20:26.140
(Ms. Yu's husband is amazing!)

00:20:26.290 --> 00:20:28.180
(Such a role model for us guys.)

00:20:39.330 --> 00:20:40.380
Are you sure it's real?

00:20:41.180 --> 00:20:42.250
No problem.

00:20:44.140 --> 00:20:44.980
Ah.

00:20:45.570 --> 00:20:47.090
Fakes are everywhere now.

00:20:47.530 --> 00:20:49.860
I don't want to get tricked like a fool.

00:20:50.180 --> 00:20:51.730
Among the people I know,

00:20:51.980 --> 00:20:52.980
if you're not the No.1

00:20:53.140 --> 00:20:55.250
person being shrewd, it's just unfair, okay?

00:20:55.250 --> 00:20:57.010
How am I being shrewd?

00:20:57.420 --> 00:20:59.180
I'm just forced by life, okay?

00:20:59.490 --> 00:21:00.620
Oh, come on.

00:21:01.460 --> 00:21:02.700
This bag looks really nice.

00:21:02.900 --> 00:21:03.860
How much did it cost?

00:21:04.140 --> 00:21:05.140
No idea.

00:21:06.140 --> 00:21:07.330
Xiu gave it to me.

00:21:09.250 --> 00:21:10.220
Knew it.

00:21:10.460 --> 00:21:12.330
Xiu's so obsessed with spoiling you.

00:21:13.290 --> 00:21:14.180
My guy should really

00:21:14.180 --> 00:21:15.460
take a few notes from him.

00:21:16.050 --> 00:21:16.900
Well,

00:21:16.900 --> 00:21:18.250
when why don't we swap?

00:21:18.900 --> 00:21:21.810
You've got the fancy car, big house,

00:21:22.380 --> 00:21:24.420
living the rich life. What's wrong?

00:21:24.620 --> 00:21:26.180
Why are you still complaining?

00:21:26.380 --> 00:21:27.700
You don't get it.

00:21:29.010 --> 00:21:30.330
Just thinking about him

00:21:32.050 --> 00:21:33.250
ticks me off.

00:21:34.460 --> 00:21:36.490
He once told me he was a rough guy.

00:21:36.940 --> 00:21:38.420
Didn't think he meant it literally.

00:21:39.530 --> 00:21:40.460
These past few years,

00:21:40.900 --> 00:21:42.250
whether it's my birthday

00:21:42.490 --> 00:21:43.330
or our anniversary,

00:21:43.460 --> 00:21:44.810
he's never remembered once.

00:21:45.460 --> 00:21:46.600
I have to remind him

00:21:46.620 --> 00:21:48.200
after work when he comes home,

00:21:48.210 --> 00:21:50.380
and he'd transfer me several grands.

00:21:50.770 --> 00:21:52.090
Like I need his money?

00:21:52.330 --> 00:21:53.770
You sound kinda privileged right now.

00:21:56.860 --> 00:21:58.420
Sometimes I think,

00:21:59.700 --> 00:22:01.980
what if I'd married Shufan back then?

00:22:02.380 --> 00:22:03.660
Would my life be better?

00:22:04.180 --> 00:22:05.290
At least he'd get me.

00:22:07.620 --> 00:22:09.220
You're still thinking about him?

00:22:09.530 --> 00:22:10.490
It's been so many years.

00:22:10.860 --> 00:22:12.220
He's probably married by now.

00:22:12.530 --> 00:22:14.140
Actually, not yet.

00:22:14.900 --> 00:22:15.900
I heard,

00:22:16.330 --> 00:22:17.860
after he left the school,

00:22:18.140 --> 00:22:20.460
he started his own tutoring center.

00:22:20.770 --> 00:22:22.460
He's swamped every day.

00:22:23.050 --> 00:22:24.250
How could he have time to date?

00:22:26.660 --> 00:22:29.700
Feels like that old line might've come true.

00:22:30.220 --> 00:22:31.660
"No one but me." right?

00:22:36.380 --> 00:22:37.250
Trust me.

00:22:38.330 --> 00:22:39.660
It's lucky you didn't marry him.

00:22:40.330 --> 00:22:41.170
Why's that?

00:22:41.290 --> 00:22:43.420
He never knew what you really wanted.

00:22:46.660 --> 00:22:48.100
(Devouring Sob)

00:22:48.100 --> 00:22:50.420
(Withered Rose in Wine)

00:22:59.250 --> 00:23:00.620
They say this pastry shop

00:23:00.730 --> 00:23:01.770
has a bit of magic in it.

00:23:02.180 --> 00:23:03.540
(Underworld Bagel)
It must be

00:23:03.570 --> 00:23:04.730
(Eros' Wish)
dark magic.

00:23:07.940 --> 00:23:10.180
Excuse me, do you have anything

00:23:10.180 --> 00:23:12.220
lighter or more refreshing to recommend?

00:23:12.420 --> 00:23:14.050
If you're not too picky,

00:23:14.050 --> 00:23:15.660
you could try our latest special:

00:23:15.810 --> 00:23:16.660
Eros' Wish.

00:23:16.810 --> 00:23:17.940
Its flavor's layered.

00:23:18.900 --> 00:23:20.250
Nothing to be picky about, right?

00:23:21.730 --> 00:23:23.810
As long as you're not allergic to love.

00:23:24.090 --> 00:23:25.940
Legend says this cake's like the world's

00:23:26.090 --> 00:23:27.570
most intoxicating love potion.

00:23:27.810 --> 00:23:30.140
The two who share it fall madly in love.

00:23:30.420 --> 00:23:32.860
They'll never part till death.

00:23:34.530 --> 00:23:36.770
Doing business in this way

00:23:36.980 --> 00:23:38.090
is pretty sneaky.

00:23:38.490 --> 00:23:39.860
I almost believed you.

00:23:40.000 --> 00:23:41.250
(Schrodinger's Box)
Faith makes it real.

00:23:41.290 --> 00:23:42.220
What if it really works?

00:23:42.700 --> 00:23:43.540
Right.

00:23:44.330 --> 00:23:45.180
I'll take that.

00:23:45.180 --> 00:23:46.140
- Then we'll…
- Excuse me.

00:23:46.570 --> 00:23:47.700
- What's this?
- Oh.

00:23:47.700 --> 00:23:49.980
Inside is a mystery dessert.

00:23:50.290 --> 00:23:51.700
Might not be your taste.

00:23:51.980 --> 00:23:53.330
Or it might surprise you.

00:23:53.660 --> 00:23:54.660
Want to give it a try?

00:23:55.330 --> 00:23:56.940
Schrodinger's Box.

00:23:58.940 --> 00:23:59.780
I'll take that one.

00:23:59.940 --> 00:24:00.810
Alright.

00:24:00.810 --> 00:24:01.650
Mm.

00:24:02.090 --> 00:24:03.660
Have you decided yet?

00:24:06.570 --> 00:24:07.620
Get me a drink.

00:24:07.900 --> 00:24:09.570
Then how about Angel's Gamble?

00:24:09.860 --> 00:24:12.380
Creamy milk tea with three lucky dice.

00:24:12.570 --> 00:24:13.940
Guaranteed sweet sorrow.

00:24:14.570 --> 00:24:15.940
Okay. Thanks.

00:24:16.490 --> 00:24:17.570
Please wait a moment.

00:24:17.770 --> 00:24:18.660
Thanks.

00:24:22.940 --> 00:24:23.980
Sorry about that.

00:24:24.290 --> 00:24:25.130
Ah?

00:24:25.430 --> 00:24:26.330
For calling you out.

00:24:26.330 --> 00:24:27.330
Am I interrupting work?

00:24:27.330 --> 00:24:28.530
Oh no, not at all.

00:24:29.090 --> 00:24:30.420
When you called me earlier,

00:24:30.620 --> 00:24:32.330
I felt like you weren't in a good mood.

00:24:32.570 --> 00:24:34.770
So I slipped out to come find you.

00:24:37.140 --> 00:24:39.530
So, is something bothering you?

00:24:41.380 --> 00:24:42.220
No, not really.

00:24:42.740 --> 00:24:44.140
I just felt like talking to someone.

00:24:44.250 --> 00:24:45.090
Oh.

00:24:45.250 --> 00:24:46.250
That's good then.

00:24:48.530 --> 00:24:49.370
By the way,

00:24:49.730 --> 00:24:50.980
don't you have work today?

00:24:52.940 --> 00:24:53.810
I…

00:24:56.180 --> 00:24:57.250
I quit my job.

00:25:04.660 --> 00:25:05.980
This shelf looks nice too.

00:25:06.620 --> 00:25:07.860
We could put one at home.

00:25:08.810 --> 00:25:10.700
Xiaoxi, maybe we can buy some frames.

00:25:11.050 --> 00:25:12.180
If you tell him,

00:25:12.660 --> 00:25:14.140
what if he breaks up with you?

00:25:14.730 --> 00:25:16.010
Then we'll put the photos

00:25:16.380 --> 00:25:17.290
all around the house.

00:25:18.900 --> 00:25:19.770
Xiaoxi.

00:25:22.700 --> 00:25:23.570
Xiaoxi.

00:25:24.220 --> 00:25:25.060
Hmm?

00:25:26.490 --> 00:25:27.380
What's wrong?

00:25:28.810 --> 00:25:29.810
Nothing.

00:25:33.490 --> 00:25:35.330
You just seemed low

00:25:35.730 --> 00:25:37.250
during dinner.

00:25:37.770 --> 00:25:38.860
Did something happen?

00:25:40.180 --> 00:25:42.010
Did I do something to upset you?

00:25:42.620 --> 00:25:44.010
Of course not.

00:25:45.290 --> 00:25:46.700
Then what's wrong?

00:25:48.380 --> 00:25:49.860
I just feel like…

00:25:51.700 --> 00:25:53.860
I should tell you about my past.

00:25:56.900 --> 00:25:58.700
If I'm not mistaken,

00:25:59.490 --> 00:26:00.940
it's about another guy, right?

00:26:02.810 --> 00:26:03.900
How did you know?

00:26:04.330 --> 00:26:06.180
I didn't. I was just guessing.

00:26:09.810 --> 00:26:10.660
Why would you suddenly

00:26:10.660 --> 00:26:12.050
bring this up with me?

00:26:12.380 --> 00:26:13.810
I think when two people are together,

00:26:13.810 --> 00:26:15.140
there shouldn't be any secrets.

00:26:16.330 --> 00:26:18.050
You have the right to know my past.

00:26:19.490 --> 00:26:20.660
But you

00:26:21.010 --> 00:26:22.730
don't really want to
talk about it, do you?

00:26:24.490 --> 00:26:25.460
No.

00:26:27.290 --> 00:26:28.730
I did hesitate,

00:26:30.570 --> 00:26:31.900
but I really wanted to tell you.

00:26:31.900 --> 00:26:33.380
It's just that I was scared...

00:26:33.940 --> 00:26:35.250
- you'd be upset if you knew.
- Listen.

00:26:35.250 --> 00:26:36.090
Listen to me.

00:26:37.860 --> 00:26:38.860
We're

00:26:39.900 --> 00:26:40.770
both adults.

00:26:41.380 --> 00:26:42.570
I know exactly

00:26:42.700 --> 00:26:43.940
what to ask and what not to ask.

00:26:44.300 --> 00:26:45.900
Besides, you don't want to talk about it.

00:26:46.180 --> 00:26:47.490
Why put yourself through this?

00:26:49.730 --> 00:26:50.940
Aren't you even

00:26:51.490 --> 00:26:52.900
the tiniest bit curious?

00:26:56.530 --> 00:26:59.330
Well, maybe just a little.

00:26:59.940 --> 00:27:01.180
But I don't want to

00:27:01.180 --> 00:27:02.940
judge the present you by the past you.

00:27:03.400 --> 00:27:05.010
I don't think that means anything at all.

00:27:05.900 --> 00:27:06.980
I only believe

00:27:07.490 --> 00:27:08.330
the you right now.

00:27:17.490 --> 00:27:18.490
And also,

00:27:19.460 --> 00:27:20.940
I can give you space,

00:27:21.180 --> 00:27:23.140
let you keep your own privacy.

00:27:23.700 --> 00:27:25.050
If you want to talk, just say it.

00:27:25.180 --> 00:27:27.090
If not, I won't ask.

00:27:27.810 --> 00:27:28.700
But,

00:27:29.330 --> 00:27:30.940
if anyone dares to mess with you,

00:27:31.180 --> 00:27:32.220
you have to tell me.

00:27:34.900 --> 00:27:37.250
Did you steal that from some CEO drama?

00:27:38.770 --> 00:27:40.660
Woman, you're playing with fire.

00:27:40.980 --> 00:27:42.770
But you've caught my attention.

00:27:42.770 --> 00:27:44.490
You're getting a little full of yourself.

00:27:44.490 --> 00:27:46.090
I've always been full of myself.

00:27:47.810 --> 00:27:49.530
Here's your Angel's Gamble.

00:27:50.530 --> 00:27:52.380
And your Schrodinger's Box.

00:27:52.770 --> 00:27:53.700
It's big.

00:27:53.700 --> 00:27:54.540
That big?

00:27:54.860 --> 00:27:55.810
How else could it fit

00:27:55.810 --> 00:27:57.900
all that honey, spices, and

00:27:57.900 --> 00:27:59.530
mysterious unknown elements?

00:27:59.650 --> 00:28:00.490
Wait,

00:28:00.490 --> 00:28:02.700
are you starting with the sales pitch again?

00:28:04.090 --> 00:28:05.090
Let me open it for you.

00:28:05.090 --> 00:28:05.930
Okay.

00:28:07.460 --> 00:28:08.300
Whoa.

00:28:08.660 --> 00:28:09.500
Wow.

00:28:10.940 --> 00:28:11.780
This…

00:28:11.940 --> 00:28:13.220
Is this really edible?

00:28:13.420 --> 00:28:14.460
More like an art piece.

00:28:14.810 --> 00:28:15.980
Of course it's edible.

00:28:16.250 --> 00:28:18.420
But you ordered the Music Box version.

00:28:19.010 --> 00:28:20.620
You can give the music crank a turn

00:28:20.620 --> 00:28:21.570
before you eat it.

00:28:21.770 --> 00:28:23.810
Music crank? Oh, then…

00:28:24.050 --> 00:28:25.700
- Here.
- Okay.

00:28:26.090 --> 00:28:27.660
- Like this?
- Yes.

00:28:30.090 --> 00:28:32.090
Please take your time and enjoy.

00:28:32.570 --> 00:28:33.940
- Thanks.
- Thanks.

00:28:44.930 --> 00:28:47.550
♪I'll stay insane♪

00:28:47.550 --> 00:28:51.330
♪When you call my name♪

00:28:54.060 --> 00:28:58.760
♪You know what I'll say♪

00:29:15.770 --> 00:29:17.830
♪At night♪

00:29:17.830 --> 00:29:22.470
♪I wonder if it will go away♪

00:29:23.810 --> 00:29:25.730
♪At dawn♪

00:29:25.730 --> 00:29:30.570
♪I wonder if I will be okay♪

00:29:31.920 --> 00:29:38.550
♪I lie awake♪

00:29:39.980 --> 00:29:40.970
Mingming.

00:29:41.010 --> 00:29:41.850
Mingming.

00:29:42.570 --> 00:29:43.420
Mingming.

00:29:43.980 --> 00:29:44.820
Ah?

00:29:45.050 --> 00:29:46.050
Are you okay?

00:29:47.290 --> 00:29:48.130
Mm.

00:29:48.140 --> 00:29:50.180
Just had something on my mind.

00:29:50.700 --> 00:29:51.570
Come on, taste it.

00:29:52.090 --> 00:29:53.220
- Yeah.
- Looks like

00:29:53.220 --> 00:29:54.420
it tastes pretty good.

00:29:55.180 --> 00:29:56.050
Sen,

00:29:58.220 --> 00:30:01.380
I don't know how to tell you this.

00:30:04.700 --> 00:30:06.570
I want to call my boyfriend.

00:30:14.980 --> 00:30:15.940
So...

00:30:17.300 --> 00:30:18.730
You've been together this whole time.

00:30:21.530 --> 00:30:23.250
Why did you lie to me?

00:30:23.620 --> 00:30:25.380
Didn't you say you broke up ages ago?

00:30:25.380 --> 00:30:26.900
What exactly do you want me to do?

00:30:38.290 --> 00:30:39.130
Oh.

00:30:41.290 --> 00:30:42.140
Fine.

00:30:42.980 --> 00:30:45.290
Guess I'll go have a cigarette then.

00:30:48.770 --> 00:30:51.050
Did you ever think about being with me?

00:30:52.420 --> 00:30:54.010
You just wanted me gone, didn't you?

00:30:54.330 --> 00:30:55.180
Stop talking.

00:30:55.180 --> 00:30:56.180
Don't push me away, okay?

00:30:56.460 --> 00:30:57.700
Stop talking.

00:30:58.010 --> 00:30:59.330
Now I finally get it.

00:31:00.770 --> 00:31:03.730
When the heart is broken, it aches so deeply.

00:31:04.330 --> 00:31:05.770
Stop it, just stop it, stop it!

00:31:05.770 --> 00:31:07.290
I hope you never have to feel

00:31:07.290 --> 00:31:08.490
this kind of pain.

00:31:10.220 --> 00:31:11.940
It's unbearable.

00:31:17.180 --> 00:31:18.500
(Mingming)

00:31:28.420 --> 00:31:30.020
(Mingming)

00:31:35.250 --> 00:31:36.140
Are you happy?

00:31:37.140 --> 00:31:38.530
Everything I told you today,

00:31:38.530 --> 00:31:39.530
he already knows.

00:31:39.530 --> 00:31:40.980
He even knows more than you do.

00:31:41.180 --> 00:31:42.490
You mean he knows everything?

00:31:42.770 --> 00:31:43.770
And he's okay with it?

00:31:44.090 --> 00:31:45.140
Yeah, he is.

00:31:45.460 --> 00:31:46.900
He's willing to wait for you?

00:31:47.050 --> 00:31:48.330
I won't make him wait too long.

00:31:49.810 --> 00:31:51.420
I'll soon be his girlfriend.

00:31:52.250 --> 00:31:53.090
What do you mean?

00:31:53.660 --> 00:31:54.730
I like Sen.

00:31:55.100 --> 00:31:56.530
I want to be with him. Is that wrong?

00:31:56.550 --> 00:31:57.490
You still like that guy.

00:31:57.490 --> 00:31:58.530
How can you be with him?

00:31:58.770 --> 00:32:00.290
Then tell me what I'm supposed to do.

00:32:00.770 --> 00:32:02.180
The reason I haven't accepted Sen is

00:32:02.180 --> 00:32:03.490
because I want to leave the past

00:32:03.490 --> 00:32:04.900
behind for good.

00:32:05.490 --> 00:32:07.250
I said I needed time. You didn't believe me.

00:32:07.250 --> 00:32:08.810
I accepted him, and you still doubt me.

00:32:09.290 --> 00:32:11.140
Why could you meddle in our relationship?

00:32:11.730 --> 00:32:13.940
You can identify all luxury items here.

00:32:14.140 --> 00:32:15.250
But what about love?

00:32:15.770 --> 00:32:17.290
You only see the selfish side of me.

00:32:17.290 --> 00:32:18.460
You don't see how much I truly

00:32:18.460 --> 00:32:19.490
care about Sen.

00:32:54.050 --> 00:32:55.140
You scared me.

00:32:55.250 --> 00:32:56.570
Good to see you're back.

00:32:58.250 --> 00:32:59.900
Look at you, love-struck and glowing.

00:33:00.220 --> 00:33:01.860
I thought you'd take forever downstairs.

00:33:02.380 --> 00:33:03.980
Well, someone's waiting for me at home.

00:33:03.980 --> 00:33:04.820
I wouldn't dare.

00:33:05.010 --> 00:33:05.850
Hmph.

00:33:07.180 --> 00:33:08.570
What's this?

00:33:09.420 --> 00:33:11.140
Matching slippers for couples?

00:33:12.010 --> 00:33:13.010
So you finally confessed?

00:33:14.050 --> 00:33:15.530
But looking at you now,

00:33:16.180 --> 00:33:17.420
you don't seem troubled at all.

00:33:18.180 --> 00:33:19.020
Mm.

00:33:21.730 --> 00:33:22.900
That's it?

00:33:25.900 --> 00:33:28.220
That means he doesn't care about your past.

00:33:28.400 --> 00:33:29.570
So what are you worried about?

00:33:30.220 --> 00:33:31.180
Does he really not care,

00:33:31.180 --> 00:33:32.730
or does he simply not want to know?

00:33:33.900 --> 00:33:34.810
And you know what?

00:33:34.810 --> 00:33:36.220
He's never told me about his past.

00:33:36.530 --> 00:33:37.370
Mm.

00:33:37.860 --> 00:33:39.940
Honestly, I'd really like to know.

00:33:40.940 --> 00:33:42.420
If he ever wanted to open up,

00:33:43.380 --> 00:33:44.460
I'd love to listen.

00:33:44.770 --> 00:33:46.940
Maybe you're overthinking this.

00:33:48.290 --> 00:33:49.220
Maybe.

00:33:52.450 --> 00:33:53.290
Listen,

00:33:53.290 --> 00:33:55.660
when we went to buy slippers today,

00:33:57.220 --> 00:33:58.140
he invited me

00:33:58.530 --> 00:33:59.770
to move in with him.

00:34:00.420 --> 00:34:01.260
Yeah.

00:34:01.700 --> 00:34:03.290
But I stalled for a bit.

00:34:03.810 --> 00:34:05.380
Then we can decorate

00:34:05.570 --> 00:34:07.530
my home in the way you like.

00:34:07.700 --> 00:34:09.460
Set it up however you like.

00:34:09.820 --> 00:34:10.780
But…

00:34:13.340 --> 00:34:14.460
But…

00:34:14.900 --> 00:34:16.650
Would you move in with me?

00:34:21.860 --> 00:34:23.980
Or I could move to your place.

00:34:23.980 --> 00:34:25.210
I just want to be with you.

00:34:25.210 --> 00:34:26.170
Sure.

00:34:26.940 --> 00:34:27.780
Really?

00:34:28.010 --> 00:34:28.850
Really.

00:34:31.900 --> 00:34:33.050
But you'll have to wait.

00:34:33.100 --> 00:34:33.980
Mm-hmm.

00:34:33.980 --> 00:34:34.820
Yeah.

00:34:34.980 --> 00:34:35.900
I need to pack up.

00:34:39.490 --> 00:34:40.380
Okay.

00:34:41.300 --> 00:34:43.420
Are you playing hard to get?

00:34:45.050 --> 00:34:45.900
I'm just worried

00:34:45.900 --> 00:34:47.490
my morning breath might scare him off.

00:34:49.820 --> 00:34:50.860
Kidding.

00:34:51.340 --> 00:34:52.690
I'm afraid that after moving in,

00:34:52.690 --> 00:34:54.820
we have different living habits,

00:34:55.170 --> 00:34:56.210
and he might question

00:34:56.210 --> 00:34:57.300
if we're that compatible.

00:34:57.780 --> 00:34:58.820
And I haven't figured out

00:34:58.820 --> 00:35:00.610
what version of me I want to show him.

00:35:01.130 --> 00:35:02.530
What a nice girl you are,

00:35:02.860 --> 00:35:04.940
yet love's turned you into a total mess.

00:35:05.740 --> 00:35:08.130
Just be yourself. What's to be afraid of?

00:35:08.820 --> 00:35:10.300
You know,

00:35:10.650 --> 00:35:12.210
maybe when Bei's home alone,

00:35:12.490 --> 00:35:14.530
he's just a sloppy guy who never showers.

00:35:16.650 --> 00:35:17.490
Think about it.

00:35:20.130 --> 00:35:22.210
Well, when I'm ready to be my true self,

00:35:23.490 --> 00:35:24.980
I'll tell him everything then.

00:35:27.210 --> 00:35:28.170
But what if...

00:35:28.740 --> 00:35:30.570
Guan actually comes after you?

00:35:31.380 --> 00:35:33.300
If she's that ruthless about it,

00:35:34.740 --> 00:35:35.940
then I'll just have to...

00:35:36.900 --> 00:35:38.820
tell Bei everything before she does.

00:35:40.420 --> 00:35:41.740
Let's settle all this first.

00:35:42.940 --> 00:35:45.050
If I'm lucky and he hasn't dumped me,

00:35:45.570 --> 00:35:47.900
I'll bring him to meet my best friend.

00:35:47.900 --> 00:35:49.130
Hey, no, no.

00:35:49.130 --> 00:35:50.690
Don't make me picture that scene.

00:35:51.130 --> 00:35:52.740
It's so embarrassing, seriously.

00:35:53.130 --> 00:35:53.970
Drop it.

00:35:54.170 --> 00:35:55.010
So, how are things?

00:35:55.260 --> 00:35:56.260
Let's talk about you.

00:35:56.900 --> 00:35:58.460
I haven't seen you lately.

00:35:58.460 --> 00:36:00.010
Something's up. Come on, spill it.

00:36:01.050 --> 00:36:03.170
The other day, my aunt set me up with a guy.

00:36:03.420 --> 00:36:04.300
Her friend's son.

00:36:04.900 --> 00:36:06.210
And the two of us

00:36:06.460 --> 00:36:07.860
got to know each other a bit.

00:36:08.300 --> 00:36:09.490
Love at first sight?

00:36:09.900 --> 00:36:11.650
No, not at all.

00:36:13.340 --> 00:36:16.130
He's really not my type. Too small.

00:36:22.780 --> 00:36:23.620
You mean his height?

00:36:24.050 --> 00:36:25.980
He's not short. Actually pretty tall.

00:36:26.460 --> 00:36:27.940
So you do like him then?

00:36:28.820 --> 00:36:30.340
No way. I told you, too small.

00:36:30.340 --> 00:36:31.420
It wouldn't work.

00:36:32.340 --> 00:36:33.980
So what if he's younger?

00:36:33.980 --> 00:36:35.530
Haven't you heard that movie line?

00:36:36.210 --> 00:36:37.300
I may be younger,

00:36:37.690 --> 00:36:39.090
but I'm taller than you.

00:36:39.530 --> 00:36:42.380
What kind of cheesy sweet talk is that?

00:36:42.380 --> 00:36:43.240
Never heard it?

00:36:43.250 --> 00:36:44.690
Nope. Where'd you even hear that?

00:36:44.690 --> 00:36:46.610
Well, you really are out of touch.

00:36:47.260 --> 00:36:48.650
Now you're totally like

00:36:48.650 --> 00:36:50.130
a girl in her first relationship.

00:36:50.610 --> 00:36:51.490
Really?

00:36:51.490 --> 00:36:53.010
I do feel silly. Is it that obvious?

00:36:53.210 --> 00:36:54.050
Yes.

00:36:54.490 --> 00:36:56.090
But it makes you kind of cute.

00:36:58.860 --> 00:37:00.830
♪In every corner of my life♪

00:37:00.830 --> 00:37:04.580
♪Quietly blooming for me♪

00:37:05.010 --> 00:37:09.010
♪I once thought I would always♪

00:37:09.010 --> 00:37:12.330
♪Stay right by her side♪

00:37:13.220 --> 00:37:17.410
♪Today we have already parted ways♪

00:37:18.820 --> 00:37:19.690
Hello, Sen.

00:37:19.700 --> 00:37:20.780
Hello, Bei.

00:37:23.090 --> 00:37:24.130
Mingming quit her job?

00:37:24.530 --> 00:37:26.460
Yes, I was going to tell you about that.

00:37:27.010 --> 00:37:29.340
But I wanted to talk to you face-to-face.

00:37:29.740 --> 00:37:30.860
I introduced her to the job.

00:37:31.460 --> 00:37:32.740
Sorry about that.

00:37:33.050 --> 00:37:34.090
No need to apologize.

00:37:35.980 --> 00:37:36.900
Then...

00:37:37.610 --> 00:37:39.090
Did she tell you why she quit?

00:37:39.240 --> 00:37:40.820
That's exactly why I came to talk to you.

00:37:41.050 --> 00:37:42.260
Are you free tonight?

00:37:43.210 --> 00:37:44.050
Yeah.

00:37:44.380 --> 00:37:45.300
Alright.

00:37:45.300 --> 00:37:46.210
Oh, right.

00:37:46.210 --> 00:37:47.300
Invite Gong and the others.

00:37:47.610 --> 00:37:48.530
See you tonight.

00:37:48.530 --> 00:37:49.610
Okay.

00:37:52.130 --> 00:37:53.420
About me and Sen...

00:37:54.170 --> 00:37:55.130
Whatever.

00:37:55.690 --> 00:37:56.570
But Bei,

00:37:56.900 --> 00:37:58.170
I hope you understand.

00:37:59.090 --> 00:38:00.650
Even if I'm not perfect,

00:38:01.210 --> 00:38:03.490
I know how to stay loyal to one person.

00:38:11.860 --> 00:38:12.860
This wiring's off.

00:38:12.950 --> 00:38:14.050
Have the technician redo it.

00:38:14.340 --> 00:38:15.180
Double-check it.

00:38:15.420 --> 00:38:16.610
Got it.

00:38:20.010 --> 00:38:20.900
Someone!

00:38:21.570 --> 00:38:22.530
Hurry, hurry!

00:38:22.940 --> 00:38:23.780
What's wrong?

00:38:23.780 --> 00:38:25.090
Give me a hand, Bei.

00:38:28.170 --> 00:38:29.010
Come on.

00:38:30.610 --> 00:38:31.610
What happened?

00:38:32.690 --> 00:38:33.820
Pulled a muscle at the gym.

00:38:34.430 --> 00:38:35.290
What do you mean?

00:38:35.290 --> 00:38:36.130
I already told you.

00:38:36.130 --> 00:38:37.050
Hide in the cabinet.

00:38:37.460 --> 00:38:38.490
Don't jump out the window.

00:38:39.300 --> 00:38:40.340
What are you talking about?

00:38:40.820 --> 00:38:42.300
I was doing squats.

00:38:42.300 --> 00:38:43.140
Squats.

00:38:45.210 --> 00:38:46.130
Come give me a hand.

00:38:47.820 --> 00:38:48.660
Hey, come over here.

00:38:49.900 --> 00:38:51.690
You're really heartless.

00:38:57.300 --> 00:39:00.010
I'm skipping tonight's dinner.

00:39:00.130 --> 00:39:01.170
Something feels off.

00:39:01.340 --> 00:39:02.380
That punk Sen…

00:39:02.490 --> 00:39:04.260
Last time he treated me was 2 years ago.

00:39:04.530 --> 00:39:05.380
Just a snack.

00:39:05.860 --> 00:39:06.730
Before he left,

00:39:06.730 --> 00:39:08.260
he even asked me for 500 yuan.

00:39:08.570 --> 00:39:10.460
Don't you think tonight sounds like a trap?

00:39:11.130 --> 00:39:13.380
He invited us to Linglong tonight.

00:39:14.610 --> 00:39:15.900
Linglong?

00:39:16.260 --> 00:39:19.090
Wow, looks like he's loaded now.

00:39:19.090 --> 00:39:21.610
Yeah, I tried calling Xiu several times.

00:39:21.780 --> 00:39:22.820
He didn't pick up any.

00:39:23.340 --> 00:39:24.260
I'm swamped today.

00:39:24.260 --> 00:39:25.490
You get in touch with him.

00:39:25.940 --> 00:39:27.300
Sure.

00:39:27.300 --> 00:39:28.140
Okay.

00:39:28.340 --> 00:39:29.980
Hey, do you think

00:39:31.340 --> 00:39:33.210
Luanluan won't pick up either?

00:39:38.860 --> 00:39:39.700
Mm.

00:39:40.690 --> 00:39:41.900
Got a task for you.

00:39:42.530 --> 00:39:43.460
Help me

00:39:44.090 --> 00:39:45.090
keep her company.

00:39:52.860 --> 00:39:53.820
Bei.

00:39:54.260 --> 00:39:55.100
Yeah.

00:39:58.820 --> 00:40:00.260
You've got nerves.

00:40:01.460 --> 00:40:03.570
Since you're like this, I gotta say

00:40:03.740 --> 00:40:04.650
something.

00:40:16.340 --> 00:40:17.780
You're buried in work all day.

00:40:17.780 --> 00:40:19.380
Your hairline receding or what?

00:40:19.980 --> 00:40:21.490
- Get lost.
- Let me check.

00:40:21.490 --> 00:40:22.420
Get lost.

00:40:22.530 --> 00:40:23.460
Slow down.

00:40:23.460 --> 00:40:25.420
My leg's pulled. Help me out.

00:40:26.090 --> 00:40:26.980
Come here.

00:40:34.481 --> 00:40:37.080
♪I'll admit♪

00:40:37.081 --> 00:40:41.120
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

00:40:42.001 --> 00:40:45.867
♪There's nothing that
I wouldn't try to do♪

00:40:45.892 --> 00:40:50.080
♪For this feeling to have you♪

00:40:50.361 --> 00:40:52.560
♪I'll resist♪

00:40:52.881 --> 00:40:54.895
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

00:40:54.920 --> 00:40:57.080
♪Your touches again♪

00:40:57.961 --> 00:41:01.941
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

00:41:01.966 --> 00:41:05.000
♪For an image of you♪

00:41:06.001 --> 00:41:08.440
♪Take my hand again♪

00:41:08.441 --> 00:41:10.200
♪Take my mind again♪

00:41:10.281 --> 00:41:13.640
♪Break into my heart again♪

00:41:14.041 --> 00:41:16.218
♪I'm falling out again♪

00:41:16.243 --> 00:41:18.080
♪I'm on my knees again♪

00:41:18.081 --> 00:41:21.920
♪To beg for the truth♪

00:41:23.761 --> 00:41:27.920
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:41:27.921 --> 00:41:32.920
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:41:33.281 --> 00:41:36.240
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

00:41:36.321 --> 00:41:39.720
♪Did it come from above♪

00:41:39.801 --> 00:41:43.560
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:41:43.801 --> 00:41:48.880
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:41:49.281 --> 00:41:51.720
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:41:51.721 --> 00:41:56.160
♪This secret of love♪